{"id":9328,"content":"<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; TEXT-INDENT: 35pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.5\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">2015</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年《炎黄春秋》杂志目前已在各地邮局开始订阅。凡需要本刊的读者，可以直接到本地邮局订阅。2015年《炎黄春秋》杂志每期定价</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">10</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">元，全年定价</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">120</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">元。<BR>　　</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: #fafafa; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">本刊将不负热爱</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">《炎黄春秋》</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: #fafafa; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">读者的期待，坚守本刊“实事求是，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;\">秉笔直书，不增美，不溢恶，求实存真，以史为鉴，以史资治”的办刊宗旨，在</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">新的一</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;\">年推出更多的精彩文章以飨读者。<BR></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\"><?xml:namespace prefix = \"o\" ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\"><o:p><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp; <SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">2014</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年《炎黄春秋》杂志具体订阅办法请参阅本网首页“订阅邮购”，内中有详细介绍：<A href=\"http://www.yhcqw.com/mall/zybdy/index.html\">http://www.yhcqw.com/mall/zybdy/index.html</A></SPAN></FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>","title":"各地邮局均可订阅2015年《炎黄春秋》杂志","time":1415529214999}